Adding visual Charts- Num of Plants By Operator Company Word chart 39

Num of Plants By Operator Company
Click on an empty space on the canvas, from the Visualization pane Select Word Chart
Fill the value fields provided below for the necessary fields
Build Visual: 
  • Category = Operator Company
  • Value = Num of plants

Format Visual:
General:
Height = 338
Width = 274
Horizontal = 1006
Vertical = 382
Title -> On
Text = Num of Plants By Operator Company
Font = Segoe UI, Size = 12
Text color = # FFFFFF
Background color = # a38600
Horizontal Alignment = Center
Background -> On
Color = #F8F6EB
Transparency = 0%
Header Icons -> on
Color-> Background = #FFFFFF, Border = #FFFFFF, Icon = #333333
Transparency = 0%
Tooltip -> On
